Description: Parallel OCR grep over images
 Runs Tesseract OCR in parallel across a directory tree and prints paths
 of images whose text matches a pattern. Supports dedup, checkpointing,
 and grep-compatible flags (-v, -c, -q, -m, -F, -i, -e, --include, --exclude).
